summary:
During the past year I have worked as HR/Administrative Assistant in one of the biggest Company within the Aerospace Industry. Thus, my competences portfolio includes all those functions used on a daily basis within most offices.
Among my strengths, I am particularly proud of my ability to take care of customers, skill that I have refined during many years working as shop manager. I also used this skill daily for my other activity, teaching.
I am used to teach languages in my spare time. My attention to customers let me understand the specific needs of my students, so  I can plan a tailored studying program for each of them. Customer satisfaction is of primary importance to me, and my drive makes me not just reaching specific objectives but I strive to exceed customer expectations over the quality output of my work.
Other strengths are definitively communication and team work, but I am also capable of working on my own. A humble and hard worker who is not afraid of new challenges.
